ight="476" srcset="https://es.wordpress.org/files/2017/02/eventos-wordpress-semana-espana.png 1280w, https://es.wordpress.org/files/2017/02/eventos-wordpress-semana-espana-300x112.png 300w, https://es.wordpress.org/files/2017/02/eventos-wordpress-semana-espana-768x286.png 768w, https://es.wordpress.org/files/2017/02/eventos-wordpress-semana-espana-1024x381.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px" /></p>\n<p><strong>¬°Buenos d√≠as a todos!</strong> Os dejamos algunas noticias y el listado de las Meetups para esta semana.</p>\n<h2>Meetups</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>24/05 &#8211; <strong>Barcelona</strong>¬†&#8211; <a href="https://www.meetup.com/es-ES/wordpressbcn/events/239426032/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Hardening WordPress like a Hacker con Chema Alonso</a></li>\n<li>25/05 &#8211; <strong>Barcelona</strong> &#8211;¬†<a href="https://www.meetup.com/es-ES/Barcelona-WooCommerce-Meetup/events/239503985/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">WPML support desk representative Yvette Oliveau, will give presentation</a></li>\n<li>25/05 &#8211; <strong>Tarragaona</strong> &#8211;¬†<a href="https://www.meetup.com/es-ES/wordpresstarragona/events/239932101/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Diferencias entre WordPress.COM y WordPress.ORG</a></li>\n<li>25/05 &#8211; <strong>M√°laga</strong> &#8211;¬†<a href="https://www.meetup.com/es-ES/WordPress-Malaga/events/240079531/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Comercio electr√≥nico en WordPress con WooCommerce (Taller)</a></li>\n<li>25/05 &#8211; <strong>Valladolid</strong> &#8211;¬†<a href="https://www.meetup.com/es-ES/Valladolid-WordPress-Meetup/events/240114536/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">WPO + RENDIMIENTO en WordPress por Rober y Rub√©n</a></li>\n<li>26/05 &#8211; <strong>Ir√∫n</strong> &#8211;¬†<a href="https://www.meetup.com/es-ES/Irun-WordPress-Meetup/events/239588904/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Presentaci√≥n del grupo de Irun WordPress Meetup</a>¬†(<em>E